      <title>墨西哥候选人在第一场辩论中就提案展开争吵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/mexico-candidates-squabble-in-first-debate-light-on-proposals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统候选人在 2024 年竞选的第一场辩论中相互攻击并试图诋毁对方，同时对解决腐败、教育和健康问题的提案细节却轻描淡写。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/mexico-candidates-squabble-in-first-debate-light-on-proposals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 05:05:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
